    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Renaming metrics is definitely not ideal and should be avoided.\r\n\r\nIf we move the dashboards need to also keep in mind tho that there are projects might get the dashboard from this repo, e.g. [eth-docker fetches it from stable branch](https://github.com/eth-educators/eth-docker/blob/1fda509a973b14f5dc7fb1bc78f5c0b7248249aa/grafana/provision-dashboards.sh#L64). There are further unknown amount of references we would probably break but might not be a big deal and would be fixed sooner or later.\r\n\r\nCould maybe consider to publish an image (`chainsafe/lodestar-dashboards`) which includes all dashboards and other projects can get them from there. This would also be a possible solution to our local metrics setup as mentioned in [this comment](https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/5123#issuecomment-1426768630).",
